{"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithm","instances":[],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Tactic.Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.Datatypes"],"declarations":[{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/b5eba595428809e96f3ed113bc7ba776c5f801ac/Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.lean#L117-L118","name":"Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.runSimplexAlgorithm","line":117,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.runSimplexAlgorithm","doc":"Runs Simplex Algorithm starting with `initTable`. It always terminates, finding solution if\nsuch exists. Returns the table obtained at the last step.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.runSimplexAlgorithm\"><span class=\"name\">Linarith</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimplexAlgorithm</span>.<span class=\"name\">runSimplexAlgorithm</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(initTable : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/Datatypes.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.Table\">Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.Table</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/Datatypes.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.Table\">Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.Table</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/b5eba595428809e96f3ed113bc7ba776c5f801ac/Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.lean#L106-L111","name":"Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.runSimplexAlgorithmImp","line":106,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.runSimplexAlgorithmImp","doc":"Implementation of `runSimplexAlgorithm` in `SimplexAlgorithmM` monad. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.runSimplexAlgorithmImp\"><span class=\"name\">Linarith</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimplexAlgorithm</span>.<span class=\"name\">runSimplexAlgorithmImp</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM\">Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/b5eba595428809e96f3ed113bc7ba776c5f801ac/Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.lean#L100-L103","name":"Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.choosePivots","line":100,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.choosePivots","doc":"Chooses entering and exiting variables using Bland's rule that guarantees that the Simplex\nAlgorithm terminates.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.choosePivots\"><span class=\"name\">Linarith</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimplexAlgorithm</span>.<span class=\"name\">choosePivots</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM\">Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></span>)</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/b5eba595428809e96f3ed113bc7ba776c5f801ac/Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.lean#L81-L94","name":"Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.chooseExitingVar","line":81,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.chooseExitingVar","doc":"Chooses an exiting variable: the variable imposing the strictest limit on the increase of the\nentering variable, breaking ties by choosing the variable with smallest index.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.chooseExitingVar\"><span class=\"name\">Linarith</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimplexAlgorithm</span>.<span class=\"name\">chooseExitingVar</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(enterIdx : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM\">Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/b5eba595428809e96f3ed113bc7ba776c5f801ac/Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.lean#L64-L75","name":"Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.chooseEnteringVar","line":64,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.chooseEnteringVar","doc":"Chooses an entering variable: among the variables with a positive coefficient in the objective\nfunction, the one with the smallest index (in the initial indexing).\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.chooseEnteringVar\"><span class=\"name\">Linarith</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimplexAlgorithm</span>.<span class=\"name\">chooseEnteringVar</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM\">Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/b5eba595428809e96f3ed113bc7ba776c5f801ac/Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.lean#L57-L58","name":"Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.checkSuccess","line":57,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.checkSuccess","doc":"Check if the solution is found: the objective function is positive and all basic variables are\nnonnegative.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.checkSuccess\"><span class=\"name\">Linarith</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimplexAlgorithm</span>.<span class=\"name\">checkSuccess</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM\">Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/b5eba595428809e96f3ed113bc7ba776c5f801ac/Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.lean#L35-L51","name":"Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.doPivotOperation","line":35,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.doPivotOperation","doc":"Given indexes `exitIdx` and `enterIdx` of exiting and entering variables in the `basic` and `free`\narrays, performs pivot operation, i.e. expresses one through the other and makes the free one basic\nand vice versa.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.doPivotOperation\"><span class=\"name\">Linarith</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimplexAlgorithm</span>.<span class=\"name\">doPivotOperation</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(exitIdx : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(enterIdx : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM\">Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/b5eba595428809e96f3ed113bc7ba776c5f801ac/Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.lean#L28-L28","name":"Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM","line":28,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Linarith/SimplexAlgorithm/SimplexAlgorithm.html#Linarith.SimplexAlgorithm.SimplexAlgorithmM","doc":"The monad for the Simplex Algorithm. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" hre